{"tid":1471261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"道乜歉？我地係要代表香港代表政府 對遊客道歉呀！","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:44:19.000Z","uid":229258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce6408bb1c3442e23752bc08686c12828783de6","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"遊客係無可否認受到影響，但責任係邊個到？我認為可以如此推論：<br />\n政府唔肯回應示威者因而行動升級，機管局亦假意取消航班影響旅客及意圖陷害示威者；所以我地要道歉，但最緊要係識<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">focus大部分責任落政府到。</span></ins> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日都有個post講過外國遊客提出既建議：<br />\n&quot;You don't need to tell people what happened, they know what happened<br />\nPeople now have smartphones and newspapers<br />\nYou need to tell people <span style=\"color: red;\">WHAT YOU WANT!</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而宜家正係一個好好既機會去tell them what we want:<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係為左自己將來利益 而係政權壓迫到我地要爭取翻<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">原本已有但消失緊</span></span>既自由同人權<br />\n<br />\n係，我地錯在要阻旅客登機，但我地已被迫到無路可走。我地只對旅客有責，而非對濫權既警察或不公義既政權有愧。<br />\n<br />\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused.<br />\nWe apologize for the incompetence of our government and Airport Authority, whose executive mishap have costed you your journey back home and invaluable time lost.<br />\nWe apologize for the unjustifiable acts of  brutality and violence by the police force towards our fellow protestors, which has made Hong Kong an unfavourable destination for travel.<br />\nWe apologize for the indifference of HKSAR government towards the opinion of 2 million citizens in the 16th June peaceful protest, which had extinguished all our hopes for a conflict-free resolution and left us no choice but to escalate our actions.<br />\nWe apologize for our actions yesterday, because that is <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">the only way left</span></strong> to show our defiance towards the injustice and oppression we have been experiencing and to make our voices heard in the international world."},{"pid":"21d18619f6fa59556df1e5e7a9920669c43e28ea","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de86d52c3880e6a87ee60c8afae11870ecfc41d8","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"文宣依邊請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44bf5241eb319a4b1f121c8b97f97799dc0dc82","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e259282ad0d2d0a554f6f67a1af149eda00fdd5","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae01026b9d664f0380d47e34f1752fc41e0f3019","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3562fcd7d5ee238c618a8112adea3cdba08c7741","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916cd8562bb3d9edf9ca46ec112591fe562219b2","tid":1471261,"uid":229258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928a46645394aadd44ac241442045671c80f0cb3","tid":1471261,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮多人不怪"}]}